          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> into halves diagonally</p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span><strong> lemon</strong> into wedges </p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> to a pot and cover them in plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\n<p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p>\n<p>Once tender, drain the<strong> sugar snap peas </strong>and return them to the pot with a <span class=\"text-highlight\">drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></span></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1793.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy</strong><strong> fish</strong> with the <strong>chips</strong>,<strong> sugar snap peas </strong>and <strong>dill mayonnaise</strong> to the side</p>\n<p>Garnish with a wedge of <strong>lemon</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
